channel.title: A comand to teleport someone somewhere
channel.description: Im looking for a command (not ::xteletome or ::xteleto) Like, type ::deathpit ipwnj00 (deathpit is the place, ipwnj00 would be a person i wat to telehim to) and it would tele ipwnj00 to a place full of monsters, or the wild. Depending on the coordinent of the code. I need help doing that.

item.title: A comand to teleport someone somewhere
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("commandname")) { teleportToX= 1111; teleportToY= 1111; }

Edit the X and Y coordinates to your liking.

[quote=“Stixx, post:2, topic:109039”]Sorry but most of us aren’t that great of coders here (unless you’re probably a senior member or higher in rank).
You can always do just ::deathpit and add in the command in the client.java with the teleport coords. :)[/quote]

It’s a very basic code.
